{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 nvk_TAKES\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 nvk_TAKES is a collection of scripts designed to improve Reaper workflows using takes, especially when making variations for game audio and sound design. Automatically embed take markers which can be used to easily shuffle through variations in files that contain more than one variation with a single keystroke. Available for purchase at https://gum.co/nvk_WORKFLOW\par}
